## Message Part Rendering

### MessagePartRenderer.tsx

Handles rendering of different message part types:

#### 1. Subagent Indicator

```typescript
const renderSubagentIndicator = (part: MessagePart, index: number) => {
  const meta = SUBAGENT_META[part.type];  // { icon, name }
