**Supported Tools**:
- `tool-generateImage`
- `tool-generateVideo`
- `tool-removeBackground`
- `tool-upscaleImage`
- And all other media tools

#### 3. Message Part Types

```typescript
switch (part.type) {
  case "text":
    return <Response>{part.text}</Response>;

  case "error":
    return <ErrorCard />;

  case "file":
